name: Decided
description: In most social situations we will probably try to do good, appear friendly, and pleasant to others, we will try to adjust to the circumstances.  But, there are some people who say that such a thing is hypocritical, we don't need to wear a "mask" in socializing.  They say that we should be able to be ourselves, and show who we are to the world.  They also think that wearing a mask in socializing is also a tiring thing.
